    <item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-core-problem-details-04.txt'>
        <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-core-problem-details-04.txt</link>
        <title>"Concise Problem Details For CoAP APIs", Thomas Fossati, Carsten Bormann</title>
        <dc:date>2022-05-25T23:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
        <description>This document defines a concise "problem detail" as a way to carry machine-readable details of errors in a REST response to avoid the need to define new error response formats for REST APIs for constrained environments.  The format is inspired by, but intended to be more concise than, the Problem Details for HTTP APIs defined in RFC 7807.</description>
    </item>
